Rider Governs.
The provisions of this Rider modify and supersede certain provisions of the commercially printed portion of this Lease to which this Rider is attached, which together constitute this Lease. In the event that any term, covenant or condition contained in this Rider shall conflict or be inconsistent with any term, covenant or condition contained in the commercially printed portion of this Lease to which this Rider is attached, then those contained in this Rider shall
trans:
Préambule du Rider.
Les dispositions de ce Rider modifient et remplacent certaines dispositions de la partie imprimée commercialement de ce Bail auquel ce Rider est attaché, lesquelles constituent ensemble ce Bail. Dans le cas où une disposition, un engagement ou une condition contenue dans ce Rider entrerait en conflit ou serait incohérente avec toute disposition, engagement ou condition contenue dans la partie imprimée commercialement de ce Bail auquel ce Rider est attaché, les dispositions du Rider prévaudront.
